Any ideas for perks go here. They should be realistic
Name: effect
*************************
Cold blooded: lets the player attempt a first-strike skill check for combat
Pack rat: improved carry capacity
Did I say that?: can re-roll charisma checks
Wild Wasteland (needs a different name): random encounters are much more likely
Salty: lets the player sail wind-powered vehicles
Scary: makes there a slight chance that enemies attempt to run away from combat even if they're properly equipped (and didn't bring a kinfe to a gunfight)
Knife to a gunfight: enemies have decreased accuracy when the player equips a melee weapon and no ranged weapon
Speedy: increased movement speed when exploring
Iron gut: risk on all foods reduced 20%
Double damage potion: all melee damage done will be doubled (it would make sense to be better at finding weak points on people or having good martial arts technique, but nobody shoots a bullet harder than anybody else)
Medeival: increased damage and rate of fire with bow and throwing weapons, as well as increased first strike chance and hunting kill chance with them.
Weakness debuff: all damage done will be halved
Rabbies: all damage increased by 1.25, but food eatten will be halved
StoneSkin: all damage decreased by 10% per hour, all food eatten will restore 100 - 10% * number of hours with the effect
CementSocks: speed decreased
Hangry: +2 charisma when over 50% fed, but -2 charisma when under 50% fed
Red Pill: Enemy ranged weapon accuracy decreased by 20%
It's a Dry Heat: improved heat resistance
You should have been here last Winter: improved cold resistance
Bear: If the player runs out of water in their inventory, they get their thirst meter refilled halfway
An Apple a Day: The player's hygeine and illness meter goes down 50% slower
Sweet: improved charisma with females
Charming: improved charisma with males
Inquisitive: more EXP from everyday actions
Quick Parry: improved block speed in combat
Shields for Arms: blocks absorb a higher percentage of damage in combat
Barter Beater: sell items for an increased cost
Senior Discount: get a reduced price on items, only if the character is old
Safe Driver Discount: Reduced chance of being attacked by bandits or wrecking the car when fast travelling in a vehicle
Sweaty: All athletic traits increase by 2 (quickness, endurance, strength, recovery), but water and hygiene levels go down faster
Grapple master: immune to grab attacks from enemies
Pitiful: Reduced chance of being robbed or maimed on a successful surrender, even if the enemy is greedy or merciless
Guitarist: unlocks the guitar instrument as playable
Drummer: unlocks the drum instrument as playable
Hairy: improved cold resistance at all times, +1 to intimidation, and -1 to seduction
Damaged but dashing: When combatHealth is below 50%, all charisma attrbutes get a +1
Pacifist: when not carrying a weapon in the inventory, all charisma and survival stats get a +1 boost
Craftsman: unlock all crafting blueprints

